LAYER_BUILDINGS_LOW_RESOLUTION

public static final GELayerId LAYER_BUILDINGS_LOW_RESOLUTION
The Layer ID of the low resolution (gray) buildings layer. Use as an argument to GEPlugin.getLayerById() or GEPlugin.enableLayerById(). Note that as photorealistic buildings continue to be created and added to the LAYER_BUILDINGS layer, the low-resolution version of those buildings will be removed from this layer. This layer will therefore change over time. 3a5bb88e-7181-11de-88da-17a790575c91
